Package com.mlt.mkt.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataConverter
    Converter from record to data and vice versa, useful to convert timed data stored in a database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Base class of timed data.
    DataList
    A list of data objects.
    DataListSource
    A data list that retrieves data from a data source backed by a persistor.
    DataRecordSet
    A recordset of time series data.
    DefaultDataConverter
    Default data converter.
    Indicator
    Indicator base class.
    IndicatorDataList
    A data list that retrieves its data from an indicator, thus calculating the data each time it is retrieved through the get method.
    IndicatorSource
    Indicator data source.
    IndicatorUtils
    Indicator utilities.
    Instrument
    Financial instrument definition.
    Period
    Periods of trading.
    PlotData
    A container for the data to plot in a JChartContainer.
    Tick
    Tick data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataType
    Enumerates the data types of a chart.
    Filter
    Enumerates the filters applicable to price data.
    OfferSide
    Enumerates the two possible offer sides, ask and bid.
    PlotScale
    Enumerate the different plot scales supported.
    PlotType
    Enumerates the types of plots, line, bar, candlestick and histogram.
    Unit
    Units used to define periods of aggregate incoming quotes.
